                        "displayName": "Joris Van den Bossche",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Brussels"
                    },
                    "body": "Good to hear that it's working! \r\n\r\nWe could certainly have better documentation regarding this, i.e. what approaches can be used when having in-memory json like data / dict, and you want to convert this to a pyarrow Table. I agree that using {{pa.array(..)}} is not necessarily the first thing you would think about. \r\n\r\n",
